description: Creates or updates the specified compute policy. During update, the compute policy with the specified name will be replaced with this new compute policy. An account supports, at most, 50 policies

compute_policy_name.description: The name of the compute policy to create or update.

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to create or update the compute policy. The max degree of parallelism per job property, min priority per job property, or both must be present.

properties.description: The compute policy properties to use when creating a new compute policy.

subscription_id.description: Get subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the Azure resource group.

account_name.description: The name of the Data Lake Analytics account.
